They come back over the barrel 5.875 from the muzzle. If the threads are the typical .625 long.

They are made from aircraft grade aluminum, finished flat, hard coat, black. Anodized to Type III Mil-Spec for a long service life. 

Our Military items are anodized at the same facility at the same time. 100% U.S.A. Designed, developed and manufactured. 

They take the place of your factory muzzle device like a FH. 

These do not lengthen the barrel. Some users have reported tighter groups due to better barrel harmonics with the increased weight.
